  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd  \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd.\u0baa\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The most hated MP by the people of the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kinniya City Councilor MM Mahdi has said that Mahindananda Aluthgamage is one of the most hated MPs in the country.",
        "The report further states that Mahindananda Aluthgamage has been subjected to the wrath and curse of the people by destroying agriculture and causing food famine and economic crisis since he was the Minister of Agriculture.",
        "Kinnia City Council Member MM Mahdi further said that people like him, who have pushed the country and the countrymen to the underworld by not being able to guide the President and the government properly, should be ashamed of the media saying that the President is talking to Russia and the United Arab Emirates for fuel."
      ],
